  <brief_title>Prospective Multicentric Study of Cytomegalovirus Resistance in Transplant Patients and Bone Marrow Recipients</brief_title>
  <acronym>PHRC CMV</acronym>
  <official_title>Cytomegalovirus Resistance in Transplant Patients and Bone Marrow Recipients in the Prophylaxis Era, a French Multicentric Cohort Study</official_title>
