        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Allogeneic bone marrow transplant recipient or solid organ transplant recipient,
             included in the cohort at the time of its firs active CMV infection (ie biological
             signs of CMV replication (viremia, ADN or ARN aemia, Antigenaemiapp65….) with or
             without fever, or clinical end organ disease symptoms

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient without medical care.policy,

          -  patient that did not signed the médical consent
      </textblock>
